title: Best of Donkey of the Day- Gravity Diagnostics
itunes:title: Best of Donkey of the Day- Gravity Diagnostics
description:
Today we flash back to when Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Gravity Diagnostics in Covington, for throwing a surprise birthday party for their employee that did not want to celebrate.
